data.title: Grettell_Valdez
data.meta_description: Grettell Valdez was born on July 8, 1976 in Mexico City, Distrito Federal, Mexico. She is an actress, known for Camaleones (2009), Clase 406 (2002) and Heridas de amor (2006). She was previously married to Patricio Borghetti.
data.text:
Grettell Valdez

Grettell Valdez was born on July 8, 1976 in Mexico City, Distrito Federal, Mexico. She is an actress, known for Camaleones (2009), Clase 406 (2002) and Heridas de amor (2006). She was previously married to Patricio Borghetti.
